Package controllers

Class ParkingReportController

java.lang.Object
controllers.ParkingReportController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientAware
public class ParkingReportController extends Object implements ClientAware
Controller for the parking report screen. Displays statistics related to user behavior using two pie charts and one bar chart: - Number of users who extended their parking - Number of users who arrived late - Duration of parking sessions (0ג€“4, 4ג€“8, 8+ hours) This screen is only available to staff roles such as attendants and managers.

    • getParkingReportFromServer

      public void getParkingReportFromServer()
      Sends a request to the server for the parking report of May 2025. This date is currently hardcoded for demonstration purposes, but it can be made dynamic in future versions.
